{
  "stem": "12053.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he summoned the Refugee Committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How he did it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got through to Manchester to the Refugee Committee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, if you don't come immediately and take all of us away, there's going to be the biggest ructions you've ever seen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The whole village will get to know about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took us all away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they reopened what was called [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Kircher ?] House.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It wasn't that far from Manchester, about an hour and a half drive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was within a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "While that row was going on, I fainted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was just 21.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was my 21st birthday that, you know, that week, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my parents came after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They arrived in the beginning of January.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But they were segregated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They weren't allowed to come to us by the British government because of fear of spies from abroad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they segregated my father and my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they asked them questions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That took three weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my mother went on hunger strike.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She said she's come to see her children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the doctor said he's not going to be responsible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He's got to release her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She's got to see her children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "For three weeks, we didn't hear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were in complete segregation, in, in isolation to be questioned by the British-- by the government.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So anyway, they came a few days after my 21st birthday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, they weren't even there, Uncle and Auntie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were in Coventry with her mother on holiday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And like a fool, we-- as soon we heard that they were coming, we wrote and told them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had one day alone with our parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
